Commands to start Flask Server:

Step 1) Open cmd in the project directory(where we have our app directory)
Step 2) Set FLASK_APP=app.py and press Enter
Step 3) set FLASK_ENV=development (if you get error use --> set FLASK_DEBUG=True)
Step 4) flask run


To create a root, create a HTML file


AJAX --> asynchronous java xml
In Flask, ajax acts as a data carrier from front end to back end.